title: Philip Pullman: La Belle Sauvage (The Book of Dust #1)
description: Philip Pullman: La Belle Sauvage (The Book of Dust #1) More info, and more ebooks download: http://www.download-books.com/philip-pullman-la-belle-sauvage-the-book-of-dust-1/ Eleven-year-old Malcolm Polstead and his dæmon, Asta, live with his parents at the Trout Inn near Oxford. Across the River Thames (which Malcolm navigates often using his beloved canoe, a boat by the name of La Belle Sauvage) is the Godstow Priory where the nuns live. Malcolm learns they have a guest with them, a baby by the name of Lyra Belacqua
